text: yeung nung banhchoul karphyokhlach tow knong chetd puok del brachheang daoysaarte kar thveu shi ri k robsa puokke champoh a l laoh daoy trong minban banhchouh phosdo tang avei( mk banhcheak) ampi vea laey . kanleng snaknow robsa puokke noh ku thanonork haey vea chea kanleng da akrak samreab puok del bampean
